.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: collecting, hiking, video-games, rock-climbing, chess, skydiving, sudoku
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, italian, pakistani, polish, russian, turkish
1. the russian is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the russian##2
3. the chinese is on the right of the australian##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the italian##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is in the middle##1
6. the polish is on the left of the australian##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the pakistani##1
9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby          | chess | video-games | skydiving | hiking | sudoku | collecting      | rock-climbing  |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | turkish     | italian     | polish  | australian | chinese |

