 3. the manager is the polish##1
 4. the german is on the left of the pakistani##1
 5. the writer is on the left of the electrician##1
 6. the indian is the nurse##1
 7. the canadian is on the left of the librarian##1
 8. the writer is between the electrician and the indian##2
 9. the canadian is on the right of the bartender##1
10. the dutch is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
