.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, juice, lemonade, sprite, tea, water
7 different games are played: domino, go, canasta, billiard, snooker, monopoly, chess
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 5. the person playing domino is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person playing billiard is between the person drinking juice and the person playing monopoly##2
 7. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 8. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is the person playing go##1
10. the person playing domino is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | juice    | sprite  | lemonade  | fanta  | water      | tea       | iced-tea |
| Game   | snooker | billiard | monopoly | chess | domino | canasta | go  |

