.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, disco, folk, house, metal, punk, rock
City: nizza, venice, hannover, rome, london, san-francisco, miami
1. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to london is the fan of disco##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is between the fan of rock and the fan of classical##2
4. the fan of punk is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is in the middle##1
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
8. the person traveling to venice is the fan of house##1
9. the fan of metal is the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | house      | metal | classical | folk | rock      | disco      | punk |
| City     | venice | san-francisco | miami       | nizza | hannover | london | rome |

