The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: rose, marigold, iris, amaryllis, aconite, tulip, dahlia
 1. the person who growstulip is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 3. the person who growsmarigold is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is between the person who growsaconite and the person who growsdahlia##2
 5. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is the person who growsaconite##1
 9. the person who growsiris is between the person who growsaconite and the person drinking iced-tea##2
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | coffee | cola    | hot-chocolate | fanta   | lemonade | milk    | iced-tea |
| Flower      | amaryllis | rose | dahlia    | marigold | aconite    | iris | tulip  |

