There 7 different types of food: broccoli, cauliflower, corn, grapes, pineapple, pomegranate, strawberry
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is in the middle##1
 3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person eating broccoli##2
 5. the person eating grapes is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person eating strawberry is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the person eating corn is the person eating corn##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
10. the person eating corn is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
| Birthday   | march       | june | september      | november | april       | october | august |
